cats.name: Tigger
cats.personality: I am a sweet and loving kitten looking for a home. I like to explore and play with my catnip toys. I would love to meet you!

cats.name: Bubba
cats.personality: I can be a little spicy with people, but I'm an excellent mouser. I am a working cat, and am looking for a job! If you have a barn or shop for me to keep an eye on, I might be the companion for you!

cats.name: Titan
cats.personality: I am a big softie who enjoys the company of people but cats, not so much. So I prefer to be the only cat in a new home.

cats.name: Fiona
cats.personality: I am a sweet and loving little lady looking for a home. I hate mornings, but I like to cuddle and take naps in warm places.

cats.name: Spud
cats.personality: I'm a rambunctious little kitten, looking for my forever home.

cats.name: Oreo
cats.personality: I am a sweet lady who needs a quieter home. I do well with other cats & older kids who know how to give me space & I need a little more time to adjust to new situations. But once I've warmed up, I love cuddles & napping.

cats.name: Cleo
cats.personality: I am ok with people I'm familiar with, but scared of strangers. I don't like being handled and I will never be a cuddly companion. I am a working cat, and am looking for a job! If you have a barn or shop for me to keep an eye on, I might be the companion for you!

cats.name: Flower
cats.personality: I am looking for a quiet home without children under the age of 12 years. The ideal home for me will be quiet and patient with me while I come out of my shell, they will love me even if I continue to be a wallflower and will give me comfy places to hide like cat beds and cat trees.

cats.name: Puss in Boots
cats.personality: I'm a very affectionate little kitty looking for a new home. I like to bask in the sun and explore. I would appreciate a home without other cats. It isn't that I don't like other cats, it is that the last one didn't like me and it made me sad and a bit fearful.

cats.name: Bobbi
cats.personality: I am a sweet and loving kitty looking for a home. I like to take naps in the sun, play with other cats and cuddle at night. I can be shy at first but I warm up quickly.
